  <brief_title>A Trial of Chemotherapy Before and After Surgery for Stage II,III Esophageal Squamous Cell Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of Chemotherapy With 5FU and Cisplatin Before and After Surgery for Stage II,III Squamous Cell Carcinoma of the Thoracic Esophagus:JCOG9907</official_title>
